ygData.subject: Re: location of sketches in or around Kaladim
ygData.msgSnippet: Hello the merchant who sells the sketches in Kelethin is located by the orc lift (ask any elf for the direction). The orc lift is the lift nearest to the orc
ygData.messageBody:
Hello

the merchant who sells the sketches in Kelethin is located by the orc lift
(ask any elf for the direction). The orc lift is the lift nearest to the orc
camps and CB. There are 2 merchants (outside-type merchants) up the lift.
One of them has the sketches.

Yati of Povar
Master Potter

From: pokes@...

I have heard that to buy sketches I have to go to Kelethin, but I have been
unsuccessful in finding the appropriate vendor there. Can somebody be so
kind as to pinpoint who or what I am looking for? Maybe a loc or
directions. I have made a 2nd character to pursue some of the things my
poor little misunderstood Gnome Necro can not do in the world of Norath.
